Controllers

authController.js   (contains the authentication logic for the login and registration pages)
courseController.js   (contains the logic for creating, updating, and deleting courses)
streamController.js   (contains the logic for creating, updating, and deleting live streams)
messageController.js   (contains the logic for creating, sending, and receiving messages)
